WEBVTT

00:05.649 --> 00:08.684
Arcee, a vehicular form
is approaching.

00:08.686 --> 00:09.752
Decepticon?

00:16.388 --> 00:18.265
Mom.

00:18.267 --> 00:20.100
Again?

00:20.102 --> 00:21.807
She worries.

00:27.016 --> 00:29.519
Hi, honey.

00:29.521 --> 00:30.857
Hey.

00:30.859 --> 00:32.465
Hey, uh...

00:32.467 --> 00:34.671
Finished my shift early
at the hospital,

00:34.673 --> 00:36.273
so I thought I'd swing by.

00:36.275 --> 00:37.877
Good to see you again, doctor.

00:39.451 --> 00:41.888
Arcee.

00:41.890 --> 00:43.957
So, where's Optimus?

00:43.959 --> 00:46.261
On a scouting mission
with Bumblebee.

00:46.263 --> 00:47.896
Sorry to disappoint.

00:47.898 --> 00:50.167
And I wore heels
and everything.

00:50.169 --> 00:51.902
Mom!

00:51.904 --> 00:53.771
That's odd.

00:53.773 --> 00:58.510
This is an extremely unusual
magnetic flux for any planet.

00:58.512 --> 01:02.882
I recognize this magnetic
signature, soundwave.

01:02.884 --> 01:04.617
And it would be unfortunate

01:04.619 --> 01:09.023
to have a Decepticon invention
such as this used against us.

01:09.025 --> 01:11.261
I will secure the weapon,
lord Megatron.

01:11.263 --> 01:13.966
Breakdown? Hah.

01:13.968 --> 01:16.603
If you can be bested
my mere humans,

01:16.605 --> 01:20.110
what chance do you have
against the Autobots?

01:20.112 --> 01:22.481
Allow me
to redeem myself, master.

01:22.483 --> 01:26.185
What I have lost
is a constant reminder

01:26.187 --> 01:29.423
that I must never again
fail you.

